The year is 1715. Pirates rule the Caribbean and have established
their own lawless Republic where corruption, greediness and
cruelty are commonplace.

Among these outlaws is a brash young captain named Edward Kenway.

Blackbeard, but also drawn him into the ancient war between Assassins
and Templars, a war that may destroy everything the pirates
have built.
